Throughout the EJSX codebase, we use ES6 patterns:

```typescript
// src/core/Path.ts - iterating over path components
for (let component of components) {
    // Process each component
}

// src/core/Http.ts - iterating over headers
for (let [key, value] of Object.entries(headers)) {
    this.setHeader(key, value)
}

